  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Here's the latest news on petrol",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Minister of Energy Kanchana Wijesekera says that the petrol ship ordered from the Indian Oil Company is scheduled to arrive in Sri Lanka between the 22nd and 23rd of this month.",
        "According to this, the minister mentioned that negotiations are being held to get a petrol ship from the Malaysian government and that there is a maximum number of orders to get the ship between the 10th of this month.",
        "Apart from this, the minister mentioned that discussions are being held with several other companies for getting a petrol ship.",
        "The minister added that the petrol ship ordered from the Indian Oil Company is scheduled to arrive in Sri Lanka on the 22nd-23rd."
      ],
